Package com.tabuto.jsimlife.charts

Class Summary
EnergyChartPanel Builds a dynamic chart shows current average Energy for each group.
GroupSizeChartPanel Shows a dynamic chart shows current Zlifes Group size.
RadiusChartPanel A dynamic chart shows current Zlifes average radius size.
SpeedChartPanel A dynamic chart shows current Zlife's Groups average speed values.
StatesChartPanel A dynamic chart shows current Zlifes states as a number of Horny, Hungry, bored and scary zlifes N.B.
